539
00:34:00.542 --> 00:34:03.306
...but I bet if he got one,
he'd pick her over us.


540
00:34:03.378 --> 00:34:05.312
- You can't be sure.
- Damn.


541
00:34:05.380 --> 00:34:08.543
Without Kousuke,
we'd only be able to toss the ball.


542
00:34:08.616 --> 00:34:10.413
You can think about that...

543
00:34:10.485 --> 00:34:12.680
...when he gets a girlfriend.

544
00:34:12.754 --> 00:34:15.222
Well, I guess if he gets one,
then that's that.


545
00:34:15.290 --> 00:34:16.518
So then Makoto...

546
00:34:16.591 --> 00:34:21.358
...how about you go out with me?
- Like I said, why are we talking about this?!


547
00:34:23.464 --> 00:34:25.227
That's what he says now...

548
00:34:25.300 --> 00:34:27.996
...but I bet if he got one,
he'd pick her over us.


549
00:34:28.069 --> 00:34:30.970
