My sister's a total idiot!


550
00:34:31.039 --> 00:34:33.837
Huh? I was just talking about Kousuke.

551
00:34:33.908 --> 00:34:35.967
Let's talk about my sister.

552
00:34:36.044 --> 00:34:38.069
