553
00:34:38.146 --> 00:34:39.807
You know, my sister...!

554
00:34:39.881 --> 00:34:41.815
You want to go out with me?!

555
00:34:44.419 --> 00:34:46.944
Don't come crying
if you change your mind...


556
00:34:47.021 --> 00:34:48.352
...and it's too late.

557
00:34:48.890 --> 00:34:50.858
You can drop the subject now.

558
00:34:51.693 --> 00:34:53.320
Huh? Makoto?

559
00:34:53.394 --> 00:34:55.259
- Get on the back.
- No thanks.


560
00:34:55.330 --> 00:34:58.128
Hey, what's the matter
all of a sudden?


561
00:35:00.168 --> 00:35:01.692
What's up with her?

562
00:35:01.769 --> 00:35:04.260
- It's your fault!
- How so?!


563
00:35:08.610 --> 00:35:11.841
I always thought you liked Chiaki.

564
00:35:11.913 --> 00:35:15.110
Didn't you say you had to
stick by him...


565
00:35:15.183 --> 00:35:19.085
...so he'd stay out of trouble?
- I might've said that before.


566
00:35:19.153 --> 00:35:22.418
Why pretend he never asked?
Just go out with him.


567
00:35:22.490 --> 00:35:24.515
- No way! No way! No way!
- Why not?


568
00:35:24.592 --> 00:35:28.756
I can't imagine Chiaki
being more than just a friend.


569
00:35:28.830 --> 00:35:29.626
If it doesn't work out...

570
00:35:29.697 --> 00:35:31.665
...just go back in time.

571
00:35:31.733 --> 00:35:35.032
- I'm sure you can do that.
- I don't need to go through with that.


572
00:35:35.103 --> 00:35:37.970
Sometimes you can fall in love with
someone who says they love you.


573
00:35:38.039 --> 00:35:39.734
It won't happen! Never!

574
00:35:39.807 --> 00:35:40.774
I see.

575
00:35:41.142 --> 00:35:43.838
So you're pretending
it never happened.


576
00:35:43.912 --> 00:35:45.379
Poor Chiaki.

577
00:35:45.446 --> 00:35:48.904
And after he got the courage
to tell you how he felt.


578
00:35:50.585 --> 00:35:54.180
But I suppose he doesn't
even realize that he did.


579
00:35:59.227 --> 00:36:02.560
Chiaki came to our school
this spring, right?


580
00:36:02.630 --> 00:36:03.426
Yeah.

