about him returning from abroad?


584
00:36:09.737 --> 00:36:13.138
I doubt it.
He's not too bright, for one.


585
00:36:13.207 --> 00:36:14.504
- Not true, huh?
- Not true.


586
00:36:14.575 --> 00:36:17.476
I wonder if something happened
to him at his last school?


587
00:36:17.545 --> 00:36:20.480
- Why don't you ask him?
- 'Cuz, I don't have his email.


588
00:36:20.548 --> 00:36:22.106
You're in the same class.

589
00:36:22.183 --> 00:36:24.413
But you're really good friends with him.

590
00:36:24.485 --> 00:36:26.453
But I wouldn't ask him
something like that.


591
00:36:26.521 --> 00:36:29.081
- And I wouldn't say we're good friends.
- That's a lie.


592
00:36:29.157 --> 00:36:32.217
It's not a lie. I mean...

593
00:36:39.167 --> 00:36:40.429
Stop it!

594
00:36:40.501 --> 00:36:43.095
- I can't stop it!
- It's all your fault!


595
00:36:43.171 --> 00:36:46.766
- They're getting back at him!
- Stop it, you guys!


596
00:36:46.841 --> 00:36:48.809
Look, he's turning his ass towards us!

597
00:36:51.179 --> 00:36:52.646
- Who shut it off?
- Huh?


598
00:36:52.714 --> 00:36:53.806
Huh?

599
00:36:54.615 --> 00:36:55.582
It's Mamiya.

600
00:36:56.651 --> 00:36:58.619
Are you about done?

601
00:37:01.356 --> 00:37:03.586
- Next time, Takase.
- See ya.


602
00:37:05.159 --> 00:37:07.992
That's pretty bad.
You're totally soaked.


603
00:37:08.296 --> 00:37:10.161
Are you all right, Takase?

604
00:37:10.231 --> 00:37:12.222
They threw cola on me yesterday.

605
00:37:12.300 --> 00:37:14.768
But I did manage
to throw a latte back.

606
00:37:14.836 --> 00:37:17.999
They came after you
because of that. Right?


607
00:37:18.072 --> 00:37:19.471
Hey, Makoto!

608
00:37:20.975 --> 00:37:25.571
Did you watch the night game last night?
That Saito sure put the squeeze on.


609
00:37:25.646 --> 00:37:26.613
Hm?

610
00:37:27.515 --> 00:37:30.746
- Did you just look away?
- No, I didn't.


611
00:37:30.818 --> 00:37:32.308
What are you up to?

612
00:37:32.387 --> 00:37:33.354
Nothing.

613
00:37:33.454 --> 00:37:37.049
What's going on? Tell me.
What's up your sleeve?


614
00:37:37.125 --> 00:37:38.592
I said, nothing!

615
00:37:39.293 --> 00:37:40.260
Huh?

616
00:37:42.363 --> 00:37:43.887
What's the matter?

617
00:37:46.868 --> 00:37:48.631
Konno, you...!

618
00:37:49.570 --> 00:37:52.767
Why'd you ask me to fry the tempura?

619
00:37:52.840 --> 00:37:55.536
Uh, well, I didn't think
that would happen!


620
00:37:55.610 --> 00:37:57.202
This is all your fault, idiot!

621
00:37:57.278 --> 00:38:01.009
What?! Who're you calling an idiot?!
Keep it up and I'll throw this!


622
00:38:01.082 --> 00:38:01.912
Hey. Come on!

623
00:38:01.983 --> 00:38:03.075
Fine! Throw it!

624
00:38:06.521 --> 00:38:08.352
Sorry. Didn't mean to.

625
00:38:09.490 --> 00:38:10.479
You idiot!

626
00:38:11.626 --> 00:38:15.221
That guy's pretty rude.
He's calling everyone an idiot.


627
00:38:15.296 --> 00:38:17.423
You're always calling me an idiot.

628
00:38:18.199 --> 00:38:20.167
Yeah, but I say it out of love.

629
00:38:24.572 --> 00:38:27.541
Where's your come back?
You're leaving me hanging.


630
00:38:27.608 --> 00:38:30.771
Isn't she a little off today?
Don't you think so, Hayakawa?


631
00:38:30.845 --> 00:38:32.972
Oh, uh... yes, indeed.

632
00:38:33.047 --> 00:38:37.177
- What's with the polite talk?
- Well, we haven't spoken much before.


633
00:39:17.625 --> 00:39:18.922
Makoto!

634
00:39:23.131 --> 00:39:24.393
She's not here.

635
00:39:24.465 --> 00:39:25.989
Why isn't she here?

636
00:39:26.067 --> 00:39:28.331
- Did something happen?
- Huh?


637
00:39:28.402 --> 00:39:29.426
No! Nothing!

638
00:39:29.504 --> 00:39:32.405
I bet you said something that
pissed her off.


639
00:39:32.473 --> 00:39:34.168
Don't say she's got big feet.

640
00:39:34.242 --> 00:39:37.700
- She's self-conscious about that.
- I said, there was nothing!


641
00:39:38.446 --> 00:39:39.413
Nothing!

642
00:39:42.950 --> 00:39:44.542
At least I don't think so...

643
00:39:45.520 --> 00:39:46.418
Whoa...!

644
00:39:49.657 --> 00:39:50.851
Toss it back!

645
00:39:54.362 --> 00:39:56.626
I can't throw while I'm thinking.

646
00:40:00.668 --> 00:40:03.102
I don't know... 
I just don't get it.

647
00:40:22.757 --> 00:40:23.856
Oh, it's just Yuri.

