1262
01:22:56.141 --> 01:22:59.076
Hey, why don't we invite them
to join us for baseball?


1263
01:22:59.144 --> 01:23:01.078
- Huh?!
- Go and ask them.


1264
01:23:01.146 --> 01:23:02.113
Why?

1265
01:23:02.180 --> 01:23:05.115
The more people we have,
the more fun it is.


1266
01:23:05.183 --> 01:23:08.448
Hey, do you even know them?

1267
01:23:08.520 --> 01:23:10.579
Kind of. And another thing...

1268
01:23:11.123 --> 01:23:11.919
Huh?

1269
01:23:11.990 --> 01:23:14.481
If you use my bicycle,
it'll cost you 5,000 yen.


1270
01:23:14.559 --> 01:23:15.321
Huh?!

1271
01:23:15.393 --> 01:23:17.520
Got that? 5,000 yen!

1272
01:23:17.596 --> 01:23:19.655
Hey! What's this about?!

1273
01:23:19.731 --> 01:23:23.360
Ask them nicely, "Would you like to
play baseball with us?" Like that.


1274
01:23:24.836 --> 01:23:26.463
- Oh, one more thing!
- Huh?


1275
01:23:26.538 --> 01:23:28.699
I appreciate you waiting for me!

1276
01:23:31.276 --> 01:23:32.140
Makoto!

1277
01:23:32.210 --> 01:23:33.006
What?!

1278
01:23:33.078 --> 01:23:34.705
Watch where you're going!

1279
01:23:36.181 --> 01:23:37.148
Sure!

1280
01:24:57.796 --> 01:25:00.128
You're late. Where's Kousuke?

1281
01:25:00.332 --> 01:25:02.300
- He's not coming.
- Huh?


1282
01:25:02.367 --> 01:25:04.335
What do you mean he's not coming?

1283
01:25:13.078 --> 01:25:14.511
Where'd you find that?

1284
01:25:14.579 --> 01:25:18.140
I mean, do you even know
what it is?


1285
01:25:18.750 --> 01:25:19.876
I do.

1286
01:25:20.652 --> 01:25:22.984
- Who told you?
- You did.


1287
01:25:23.054 --> 01:25:26.820
I didn't tell you.
I would never tell you.


1288
01:25:27.225 --> 01:25:29.318
You told me everything.

1289
01:25:29.394 --> 01:25:33.660
About the future you live in,
and what this is...


1290
01:25:33.865 --> 01:25:34.832
Everything.

1291
01:25:35.200 --> 01:25:36.792
H
- Hey...

1292
01:25:37.936 --> 01:25:39.426
Just as I thought.

1293
01:25:39.905 --> 01:25:41.338
Thank goodness.

1294
01:25:41.539 --> 01:25:43.507
Where did you come from?

1295
01:25:44.209 --> 01:25:45.301
The future.

1296
01:25:45.377 --> 01:25:47.675
- Can you leap?
- Not anymore.


1297
01:25:47.913 --> 01:25:49.881
Did I tell you all that?

1298
01:25:49.948 --> 01:25:50.915
Yup.

1299
01:25:50.982 --> 01:25:53.212
- And you believed me?
- Yup.


1300
01:25:53.285 --> 01:25:55.185
- You're an idiot.
- Maybe.


1301
01:25:55.253 --> 01:25:57.346
And you came back to tell me that?

1302
01:25:57.422 --> 01:25:58.320
Yeah.

1303
01:26:04.930 --> 01:26:08.195
Why did I tell you? 
I'm such an idiot!

1304
01:26:57.449 --> 01:27:01.078
That painting.
Go back to the future and enjoy it.


1305
01:27:02.554 --> 01:27:05.580
It's not going to get lost or
burned anymore.


1306
01:27:07.392 --> 01:27:12.591
I'll do my best to make sure
it's there for you in your era.


1307
01:27:13.832 --> 01:27:16.494
Sure, I'd appreciate that.

1308
01:27:20.071 --> 01:27:24.269
I was supposed to go back,
but before I knew it, it was summer.


1309
01:27:26.111 --> 01:27:29.774
I was just having
too much fun with you guys.


1310
01:27:32.550 --> 01:27:34.780
That's not how you put it.

1311
01:27:35.587 --> 01:27:37.054
Then what did I say?

1312
01:27:42.027 --> 01:27:42.994
Hm?

1313
01:27:46.564 --> 01:27:48.191
I'm not telling.

1314
01:27:48.666 --> 01:27:50.293
Why not?

1315
01:27:51.269 --> 01:27:53.737
Come on. What did I say?

1316
01:27:54.472 --> 01:27:55.803
I'm not telling.

1317
01:27:55.874 --> 01:27:59.332
You have to tell me.
I have to know now. Come on!


1318
01:28:00.245 --> 01:28:01.712
Hey, look at the lovers.

1319
01:28:02.547 --> 01:28:04.344
Look at the lovers.

1320
01:28:04.416 --> 01:28:07.510
- Well, are we in love or what?
- Look at the lovers.


1321
01:28:07.585 --> 01:28:08.643
Get lost, you idiots!

1322
01:28:08.720 --> 01:28:12.679
- Let's get out of here!
- Hurry!


1323
01:28:24.836 --> 01:28:26.804
Give my regards to Kousuke.

1324
01:28:26.871 --> 01:28:29.567
Tell him I'm sorry
I couldn't say good-bye to him.


1325
01:28:29.641 --> 01:28:30.471
Sure.

1326
01:28:32.177 --> 01:28:35.943
Oh, and... Makoto?

1327
01:28:41.052 --> 01:28:41.916
What?

1328
01:28:43.188 --> 01:28:46.555
There's something I've been
meaning to tell you.


1329
01:28:50.662 --> 01:28:52.186
Just don't...

1330
01:28:55.300 --> 01:28:58.030
Just don't get yourself hurt
by jumping out in front of things.


1331
01:29:01.039 --> 01:29:02.301
Huh?!

1332
01:29:02.373 --> 01:29:05.934
I mean, you really need to be
more careful. Be more observant.


1333
01:29:06.010 --> 01:29:09.707
Think about what you're doing
before you act. Yeah.


1334
01:29:09.948 --> 01:29:10.915
What's that?

1335
01:29:11.416 --> 01:29:13.907
That's the last thing you have
to say to me?


1336
01:29:13.985 --> 01:29:16.613
You idiot, I'm just worried about you.

1337
01:29:20.625 --> 01:29:23.958
Fine, then! Thank you so much
for worrying about me!


1338
01:29:24.028 --> 01:29:25.859
Now, just go already!

1339
01:29:25.930 --> 01:29:27.397
What are you upset about?!

1340
01:29:27.465 --> 01:29:29.057
Just go!

1341
01:29:30.835 --> 01:29:31.665
See ya.

1342
01:29:32.504 --> 01:29:33.334
See ya!

1343
01:30:09.407 --> 01:30:11.705
I wonder why...

1344
01:30:46.578 --> 01:30:48.546
I'll be waiting for you in the future.

1345
01:30:54.285 --> 01:30:57.982
Okay. I'll be right there,
I'll come running.


1346
01:31:30.488 --> 01:31:31.512
Makoto...

1347
01:31:33.958 --> 01:31:35.016
Makoto...!

1348
01:31:37.362 --> 01:31:39.023
Hey, Makoto!

1349
01:31:51.042 --> 01:31:52.839
What's going on?

1350
01:31:52.910 --> 01:31:54.138
It's one thing not to tell me...

1351
01:31:54.212 --> 01:31:56.271
...but nothing to you either?

1352
01:31:56.347 --> 01:31:58.372
All of a sudden
he's dropping out...


1353
01:31:58.449 --> 01:32:00.883
...so he can study abroad?

1354
01:32:00.952 --> 01:32:02.385
Give me a break!

1355
01:32:03.087 --> 01:32:06.056
Oh! Sorry!

1356
01:32:08.559 --> 01:32:10.322
Don't worry about it, Kaho.

1357
01:32:10.695 --> 01:32:13.664
He probably found
something he wanted to do.


1358
01:32:14.098 --> 01:32:16.896
Did he tell you something?

1359
01:32:16.968 --> 01:32:18.765
Nothing, really.

1360
01:32:20.338 --> 01:32:23.273
- There!
- Whoa!


1361
01:32:23.341 --> 01:32:25.673
- Sorry!
- Kaho, your arm's too weak...


1362
01:32:26.377 --> 01:32:27.571
Oh, boy...

1363
01:32:27.912 --> 01:32:31.177
I've also decided on what
I'm going to do.


1364
01:32:31.249 --> 01:32:33.274
Really? What?

1365
01:32:33.351 --> 01:32:35.148
It's a secret!

1366
01:32:35.219 --> 01:32:37.710
Huh? What's that about?

1367
01:32:39.057 --> 01:32:40.820
Maybe some other time.

1368
01:33:16.461 --> 01:33:18.622
Miss Konno!

1369
01:33:18.796 --> 01:33:19.660
Hey!

1370
01:33:21.032 --> 01:33:22.021
There!

1371
01:33:25.770 --> 01:33:27.294
Good throw!

1372
01:33:28.606 --> 01:33:29.971
Here it comes!

1373
01:33:31.676 --> 01:33:32.643
There!

1374
01:33:35.079 --> 01:33:42.652
The Girl Who Leapt Through Time

1375
01:33:55.166 --> 01:34:01.435
<i>As you ran around the baseball field</i>

1376
01:34:01.706 --> 01:34:07.611
<i>You seemed freer than
the clouds in the sky</i>


1377
01:34:08.112 --> 01:34:14.415
<i>Even your blocky writing in your notebook</i>

1378
01:34:14.786 --> 01:34:20.816
<i>Seemed like a light that lit everything</i>

1379
01:34:23.428 --> 01:34:29.628
<i>I didn't understand the emotion of love</i>

1380
01:34:30.034 --> 01:34:35.267
<i>This moment in time that will never return</i>

1381
01:34:35.606 --> 01:34:45.606
<i>Taught me the true meaning of love</i>

1382
01:34:48.085 --> 01:34:54.513
<i>I'm going to burn into my heart
the memories of days I spent with you</i>


1383
01:34:54.592 --> 01:35:00.827
<i>So I never have to remember them</i>

1384
01:35:00.965 --> 01:35:07.427
<i>Even if I someday fall
in love with someone else</i>


1385
01:35:07.505 --> 01:35:17.505
<i>You will always be special and precious</i>

1386
01:35:18.082 --> 01:35:26.888
<i>And this season will come around again</i>

1387
01:35:27.191 --> 01:35:33.255
<i>The fact that I met you
in the vastness of time</i>


1388
01:35:33.664 --> 01:35:39.762
<i>Has made me stronger than anything else</i>

1389
01:35:40.071 --> 01:35:46.306
<i>Running towards tomorrow in a daze
and I just so happen to get there</i>


1390
01:35:46.744 --> 01:35:56.744
<i>You will always be special and precious</i>

1391
01:35:57.421 --> 01:36:06.352
<i>And this season will come once more</i>

1392
01:36:28.052 --> 01:36:38.052
<i>That summer you promised
me that you'd never forget</i>


1393
01:36:40.331 --> 01:36:50.331
<i>Time has passed, and only
now my tears begin to flow</i>


1394
01:36:57.248 --> 01:37:03.778
<i>I'm going to burn into my heart
the memories of days I spent with you</i>


1395
01:37:03.854 --> 01:37:10.020
<i>So I never have to remember them</i>

1396
01:37:10.394 --> 01:37:16.731
<i>Even if I someday fall
in love with someone else</i>


1397
01:37:16.867 --> 01:37:26.867
<i>You will always be special and precious</i>

1398
01:37:27.845 --> 01:37:36.913
<i>And this season will come around again</i>